<p>There are more important questions than =E2=80=9CDid we reach statistica=
l significance?=E2=80=9D</p>



<p>Your A/B testing results do not, and should not, exist in their own isol=
ated universe. Keep in mind the other factors that affect how your results =
will be used: <strong>the practical significance of your results and how th=
ey influence business decisions</strong>.</p>


